=Description=

"The challenge enlisted the help of participants around the world in digging up information on open data in their city and region and contributing it to the newly launched city section of the Open Data Census. The results have been impressive with information about data on more than 20 cities from Uruguay to Germany, US to Brazil. You can see the full results in the [http://census.okfn.org/city/ City Census dashboard]."
(http://blog.okfn.org/2013/03/05/the-open-data-census-challenge-on-open-data-day-2013/)


